            <tr>
                <td align="right" width="25%">
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <br>
                        <h4>What You'll Be Doing:</h4>
                    </font>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <br>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Delivering food via bicycles</li>
                            <li>Providing excellent customer service to both our restaurant partners and their customers</li>
                            <li>Helping us field-test our software and smartphone app and providing constant feedback to our developers and team</li>
                        </ul>
                    </font>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="right">
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <h4>The Ideal Candidate:</h4>
                    </font>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Enjoys riding bikes and can ride for up to 8 hours</li>
                            <li>Wants to work a part time or full time schedule with guaranteed hours</li>
                            <li>Must possess good communication skills and be able to work well with others</li>
                            <li>Must have a great attitude</li>
                            <li>Loves to learn and collaborate within a team</li>
                            <li>Is comfortable with technology (you'll be working with a smartphone)</li>
                            <li>Is at least 18 years old</li>
                            <li>Has US work authorization</li>
                            <li>Must be able to read and take direction in English</li>
                            
                        </ul>
                    </font>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="right">
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <h4>Perks and Benefits:</h4>
                    </font>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Compensation is paid hourly and averages between $13-$16 an hour</li>
                            <li>We provide all of the equipment you need to do your job, including the phone and bike</li>
                            <li>Scheduled shifts designed around order demand to keep you busy when you're working</li>
                            <li>Career advancement opportunities</li>
                            <li>W2 Employment -- allows us to train you to do your job well, cover your medical bills in the case of an injury on the job, and prevents you from owing quarterly contractor tax bills</li>
                            <li>You'll be working in a modern environment -- time goes fast!</li>
                        </ul>
                    </font>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="right">
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <h4>This Job is Perfect For:</h4>
                    </font>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <font face="Roboto, Helvetica" color="#272727" size="3">
                        <ul>
                            <li>People with experience in the restaurant/hospitality industry (previous food delivery experience a huge plus)</li>
                            <li>People with excellent customer service skills</li>
                            <li>People who are physically active and love to be outside</li>
                            <li>People who are looking to grow with a company</li>
                        </ul>
                    </font>
                </td>
            </tr>
